data.name: TextBox5.Text
data.value: -> Valid for one (1) slot of All Event Package: Catering Service and Food by J&Js Kitchen Catering Co. -> For 50 Persons -> Complete Catering Amenities, Food and Service at a very affordable price -> Take the hassle out of catering at your next party, gathering or corporate event -> Enjoy more time mingling and working the crowd and less time preparing and cooking -> Feed the guests with mouth-watering and good quality food that are all exceptionally and hygienically prepared -> All event packages is great for occasion such as Birthdays, Corporate Events, Reunions and Parties

data.name: TextBox3.Text
data.value: Well, now you can celebrate easily with today’s deal: All Event Package that includes Catering Service, Food and Refreshing Drinks catered to you on your special occasion by J&Js Kitchen Catering for as low as PHP15000 for 50 persons.

data.name: TextBox2.Text
data.value: Your party isn’t a party until you serve food to your guests—not just any food though. Let J&Js Kitchen Catering help you out in throwing the best party with their Catering Package that will surely complete your event preparation.

data.name: TextBox15.Text
data.value: ->Basic Sound system for kiddie and birthdays PHP 2,500.00 ->Basic Sounds System with one disco light PHP 3,000.00 ->LCD Projector PHP 2,000.00 ->Professional Sounds Lights with LCD projector PHP 8,500.00 (transportation charge applicable) ->Professional Sounds Lights PHP 7,000.00 (transportation charge applicable) ->Host / EMCEE PHP 3,500.00 ->Dessert Buffet PHP 5,500.00 ->Mobile bar PHP 8,000.00 (transportation charge applicable)

data.name: TextBox9.Text
data.value: ->Floral centerpiece on all tables ->Floral centerpiece for Buffet Table ->Full silverware, glassware, and folded table napkins ->Table with floor length and elegant white cloth with topper as per motif ->Monobloc chairs with floor length white cover and ribbons as per motif

data.name: TextBox17.Text
data.value: For bookings less than 100 persons, a “below minimum charge" of PHP1,500.00 will be applied All packages are subject to PHP1,000.00 Transportation Charge, except venues located in Caloocan City Additional Transportation fee for out of town venues and those located in North/South Area depending on the distance ->10% of the contract price will be charged upon “early” cancellation of the contract ->20% of the contract price will be charged upon cancellation made a week before the event date ->50% of the contract price will be charged if cancellation is made one day before the event date ->100% of the contract price will be charged if cancelled on the day of the event date ->Any losses, breakage, gate entrance fee will be charged to the client ->Any Subdivision fee and/or CATERER’S BOND should be shouldered by the client ->Service of staffs are up to four (4) hours only, Overtime Fee of PHP100.00 per hour per staff including the driver will be charged to the client ->Additional PHP50.00 per floor per staff if the event is held in a building without service elevator or if the loading area is 50 meters away from the venue ->Lechon Corkage of PHP500.00 per piece ->Additional (List of choices is available upon request): Main Dish - PHP50.00/head Soup - PhP20.00/head, Pasta, Noodle and Vegetables - PHP40.00/head
